<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-53-0441 </DOCNO><TEXT>An international workshop on PFBC was arranged in Stockholm 22 to 24 October1986 under IEA auspices. The final report from that meeting has previouslybeen published by the National Energy Administration. One of the itemsagreed upon was to produce a brochure on the present PFBC facilitiesin the world. Sweden undertook responsibility for compiling the informationand for publishing it. The information contained in the brochure representsthe situation during the first half of 1987, when most of the informationwas received.</TEXT></DOC>